<title type="html"><![CDATA[2/5(Sun.)Taiwan's baseball culture (Host:Leroy)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=694&amp;p=722#p722"><![CDATA[
2/5 .  zoom meeting <br />host: Leroy<br />Regarding the first topic: Taiwan's baseball culture, as far as I know, when I was young, when I talked about baseball, everyone was watching junior baseball games.  People all over the country are excited about it.  As far as I know, there are six professional baseball teams in Taiwan, namely CITIC Brothers, Fubon Titans, Uni-President Lions, Lotte Tao Monkeys, and Taigang Eagles.  Wei Chan dragon , this is the name of a professional baseball team I know, if you know Taiwan's baseball culture, please tell everyone!  thank you all<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://youtu.be/OlEhRTTI98k">https://youtu.be/OlEhRTTI98k</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Sect.1. questions <br /><br /> 1. Do you like baseball?  Why?<br /><br /> 2.have you ever played baseball of any kind?<br />3,Do you know anything about Taiwan Professional Baseball? Can you share your experience?<br />4,Have you ever bought tickets to a professional baseball game? Can you share your experience!<br /><br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:10 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40 pm Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://youtu.be/D3nXXrVLzvE">https://youtu.be/D3nXXrVLzvE</a><!-- m --><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://youtu.be/6j223GGFVKQ">https://youtu.be/6j223GGFVKQ</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Sect.2.<br /> introduce the characteristics of Taiwan's railways!<br />The  second topic; Taiwan's railway system!  As far as I know, Taiwan’s railway system is divided into Taiwan Railway; there are Taroko, Puyuma,Zicang, Juguang, Fuxing, and local trains, etc. Taiwan’s high-speed rail also has business class trains.  And the economy class trains !in addition, there is the Alishan Railway on the Alishan , and finally there is the Taiwan Sugar Railway. There are sightseeing trains that you can take. This is the railway system that I know!  But have you heard of King’s Old Train DT668? If you know, can you share it with everyone? Thank you!<br /><br /><br />questions :<br />1,Do you like the trains?  Why?<br />2,Do you know what types of trains there are in Taiwan?<br />3,Have you traveled on a traditional old steam train before?<br />4,Have you ever taken a foreign high-speed rail or train abroad?  Such as Japan's bullet train!  Can you share it! Thank you<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=48">dora</a> — Sun Jan 29, 2023 9:38 pm</p><hr />
